description: A small anti-police demonstration in a north London neighborhood spiraled into looting and violent clashes that left 26 police officers injured and led to 55 arrests.
title: Rioting in Tottenham
title_page: Rioting in Tottenham - The New York Times
maintext:
Slide 1 of 9,
Residents of Tottenham, in northern London, looked at the still-smoldering remains of a building on Sunday. A small antipolice demonstration in the neighborhood spiraled into looting and violent clashes.
